  <chr>              <dbl>
1 b_Intercept       0.324 
2 b_weight0         0.0488
3 sigma             0.237 
```
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
initial_table_wide |> 
  left_join(posterior_sd) |> 
  relocate(
    posterior_sd,
    .after = .value
  ) ->
  final_report_table

final_report_table
```

